channel.title: Rate Yourself on How Much HTML You Know
channel.description: Rate yourself on a scale of 1 to 10. 10 being a Master, and 1 being you know what means. I rate myself as a 4. I am stilling learning, but I know a pretty good bit and have made websites off of what I know.
